---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Community Guidelines - Boomger."
  slug="guideline"
  description="Read Boomger’s Community Guidelines outlining acceptable behavior, safety standards, and rules designed to keep the platform respectful and secure for everyone."
>
  <main
    class="pt-10 pb-24 mx-6 sm:mx-12 lg:mx-24 max-w-5xl text-zinc-900 leading-relaxed"
  >
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Boomger Community Guidelines
      </h1>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Welcome to Boomger. Our goal is to create a safe, inclusive, and
        respectful space where meaningful connections and healthy communities
        can thrive. These Community Guidelines are designed to protect all users
        and promote positive interactions across profiles, messaging, and
        location-based communities.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        By using Boomger, you agree to follow these guidelines. Violations may
        result in warnings, temporary suspension, or permanent account
        termination.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Respect and Kindness</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Be Respectful:</strong> Treat all users
        with dignity and respect. Discrimination, hate, threats, abusive
        language, or demeaning behavior will not be tolerated.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">No Harassment:</strong> Harassment,
        bullying, stalking, intimidation, or repeated unwanted contact is
        strictly prohibited. Respect personal boundaries at all times.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Authenticity and Honesty</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Be Yourself:</strong> Use your real
        identity and authentic photos. Impersonation, fake accounts, or
        misleading profiles are not allowed.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Honest Representation:</strong> Provide
        accurate information about yourself, including age, gender, and personal
        details. Misrepresentation undermines trust within the community.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Safety and Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Protect Personal Information:</strong> Do
        not publicly share sensitive personal information such as home address,
        phone number, financial details, or private documents — yours or anyone
        else’s.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Report Suspicious Activity:</strong>
         Report scams, fraud, catfishing, or suspicious behavior using Boomger’s
        in-app reporting tools or by contacting our support team.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Appropriate Content</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900"
          >No Explicit or Inappropriate Content:</strong
        > Do not post, share, or request explicit, pornographic, or sexually
        graphic content. Boomger is intended for respectful dating and social
        interaction.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">No Hate or Violence:</strong> Content that
        promotes or encourages hatred, violence, or discrimination based on
        race, ethnicity, nationality, religion, gender, sexual orientation, or
        disability is strictly prohibited.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Respect Intellectual Property:</strong>
         Only share content you own or have permission to use. Copyright
        infringement is not allowed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Interactions and Communication</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Consent Comes First:</strong> All
        interactions must be consensual. If someone declines to engage or asks
        you to stop, respect their decision immediately.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">No Spam or Manipulation:</strong>
         Spamming, mass messaging, scams, solicitation, or attempts to
        manipulate users for personal gain are prohibited.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Legal Compliance</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Follow the Law:</strong> You must comply
        with all applicable local and international laws when using Boomger.
        Illegal activity of any kind is not permitted.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Age Requirement:</strong> Boomger is
        strictly for users aged 18 and above. Misrepresenting your age will
        result in account removal.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Reporting and Enforcement</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Report Violations:</strong> If you
        experience or witness behavior that violates these guidelines, report it
        through the app or contact us at
        <a
          href="mailto:info@boomger.com"
          class="underline font-medium hover:text-black">info@boomger.com</a
        >.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Consequences:</strong> Violations may
        result in content removal, warnings, temporary suspension, or permanent
        termination, depending on severity and repetition.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">8. Safety Tips</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Meet Safely:</strong> Choose public places
        and inform someone you trust.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Trust Your Instincts:</strong> If
        something feels unsafe, disengage and report.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Secure Your Account:</strong> Use strong
        passwords and protect your login details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">9. Community Engagement</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Positive Participation:</strong> Encourage
        respectful dialogue.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Respect Diversity:</strong> Be open-minded
        toward all backgrounds.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">10. Updates and Changes</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Stay Informed:</strong> Continued use of
        Boomger means you accept updates to these guidelines.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <p class="text-zinc-800 font-medium">
        Boomger is built on trust, respect, and real connections. By following
        these guidelines, you help create a safer and more meaningful experience
        for everyone.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
